item.title: Naval Outift?
item.dc:creator: @iceman21 iceman21
item.description:
@iceman21 wrote:

TO POST PICS:

  1. Get the picture by taking a screenshot by pressing “prtsc” that button is on the keyboard. it should say something like “prtscr” with “sysrq” under it in small letters.
  2. Open up paint and press “CTRL + V” at once now you should have the image in paint. SAVE IT
  3. Open up the internet and go to photobucket.com make a account there. Once you made the account upload that screenshot you just made.
  4. Now that you have it uploaded it should have 3 things under the pic. “Tag” “URL” and something else you just need the image url.
  5. Now go to the page with the reply thing and click image. it should come up with like in between those to put the image url and post and ure done
